A march is being held in Scenery Park to remember the lives lost in the Enyobeni Tavern tragedy this past weekend. eNCA senior reporter, Aviwe Mtila has more from Scenery Park. Courtesy of #DStv403 SCENERY PARK - A march is being held in Scenery Park to remember the lives lost in the Enyobeni Tavern tragedy this past weekend. A total of 21 teenagers died. WATCH | Inside Enyobeni Tavern where 21 teens died The circumstances leading to their deaths are still being investigated. A mass funeral for the teens is being planned for next week.